{"id":53761,"title":"[Two cases of medicinal treatment of diabetic post treatment painful neuropathy].","abstract":"Painful diabetic neuropathy is a common, difficult-to-manage complication of diabetes. We report two case of intractable painful diabetic neuropathy which occurred after the rapid lowering of blood sugar level. Although pregabalin, antidepressants, opioid analgetics and various nerve block did not improve their pain, clomipramine dramatically reduced their pain.","date":"2014-02-06","categories":"Endocrine System Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24498768","annotations":[{"name":"Diabetic neuropathy","weight":0.840845,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diabetic_neuropathy"},{"name":"Opioid","weight":0.821773,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Opioid"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.808582,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Nervous system","weight":0.801843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nervous_system"},{"name":"Diabetes mellitus","weight":0.799906,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Diabetes_mellitus"},{"name":"Complication (medicine)","weight":0.79352,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Complication_(medicine)"},{"name":"Blood","weight":0.7902,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blood"},{"name":"Peripheral neuropathy","weight":0.787886,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peripheral_neuropathy"},{"name":"Blood sugar","weight":0.77844,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blood_sugar"},{"name":"Antidepressant","weight":0.768171,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antidepressant"},{"name":"Analgesic","weight":0.745929,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Analgesic"},{"name":"Pain","weight":0.701843,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pain"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.587222,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"},{"name":"Pregabalin","weight":0.563317,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pregabalin"},{"name":"Nerve block","weight":0.435303,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nerve_block"},{"name":"Sugar","weight":0.264844,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sugar"},{"name":"Chronic pain","weight":0.221435,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chronic_pain"},{"name":"Clomipramine","weight":0.210579,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clomipramine"},{"name":"Sugars in wine","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sugars_in_wine"}]}
